{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1ca8ed2e69","title":"对王世英家属来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"97b8762435","index":0,"year":1975,"month":12,"day":13,"articleId":"1ca8ed2e69"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[{"id":"2cd1c20a34","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"1ca8ed2e69","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":".王世英，原任中共中央监察委员会专职委员。“文化大革命”中受到江青、康生的远陷道害，1968年3月含宽逝世。1979年，中共中央决定为他平反昭雪、恢复名誉。"},{"id":"dd8fc8614f","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"1ca8ed2e69","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王世英的妻子李果毅1975年12月8日给毛泽东写信说，“我自1927年入党后，对主席、对党一直是热爱的”。我身体一直不好，近年来惠了半身不遂。“希望能在我生前见到王世英的结论，请主席在百忙中能过问一下。”毛泽东的批语，写在中共中央办公厅1975年12月12日印的这封来信摘要上。"},{"id":"bb354bc0bc","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"1ca8ed2e69","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"汪，指汪东兴，当时任中共中央政治局委员、中央办公厅主任。1975年12月13日，他接到毛泽东的批示后，提出“送中央专案一办报审查结论”。"}],"contents":[{"id":"fbce2434cc","type":"title","text":"对王世英“家属来信的批语？","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"1ca8ed2e69"},{"id":"2cd1c20a34","type":"paragraph","text":"请汪的处。B","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"1ca8ed2e69"},{"id":"dd8fc8614f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"1ca8ed2e69"},{"id":"bb354bc0bc","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十三日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"1ca8ed2e69"}],"page":{"id":"1612cfb106","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"1ca8ed2e69","start":125,"end":125}}}},"__N_SSG":true}